T1  - Investment and the Cross-Section of Equity Returns
AU  - CLEMENTI, GIAN LUCA
AU  - PALAZZO, BERARDINO
Y1  - 2019/02/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/jofi.12730
T2  - The Journal of Finance
